sentences.english: Only the so-called exploitation rights are transferrable .
sentences.chinese: 只有所謂的利用權是可以移轉的。

sentences.english: Any change in the angle of attack immediately transfers into a change in the control pressure of the brakes.
sentences.chinese: 任何攻角的變化立即移轉到剎車控制壓力的變化。

sentences.english: Transferring the ownership of the subject-matter is the basic obligation for seller to performance.
sentences.chinese: 出賣人移轉標的物所有權系其應當履行的基本義務。

sentences.english: Transfer of property right included in B/L should be recognized as a new method of delivery:draft system delivery.
sentences.chinese: 提單物權移轉應當是一種新的交付方式一擬製交付。

sentences.english: It's not necessary to transfer the possession of letters patent for the creation of the pledge right of patent right.
sentences.chinese: 專利權質權的設定不以移轉專利證書的佔有爲必要。

sentences.english: This house was transferred to his wife's name.
sentences.chinese: 這棟房子已經移轉到他太太名下了。

sentences.english: Mr. Taylor relegated his project to his son after he has retted .
sentences.chinese: 泰勒先生退休後把他的事業移轉給兒子。

sentences.english: Can we transfer this agreement to a third party?
sentences.chinese: 我們可否將合約移轉給第三方？

sentences.english: The industry life cycle will influence the technology transfer ring's antitype.
sentences.chinese: 產業生命週期會影響技術知識移轉類型。
